---
title: Parmesan, Mushroom & Basil Pesto Risotto with Pine Nut Pangrattato & Parsley
description: Mushrooms, Parmesan cheese and basil pesto have a soft and lovely touch that can bring comfort to any dinner they’re invited to. Invite them to join this risotto popping with leek and a pine nut pangrattato for a night of flavour and tranquillity.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64ab44bb57da307c4116c7ef-4cd8bf8d.jpeg
